{
  "texts": [
    "The format of the dataset is identical to that of the Alpaca data, with higher-quality generated answers.",
    "• Alpaca GPT4 data zh (Peng et al, 2023).",
    "The Alpaca GPT4 data zh dataset translates the instruction inputs from the Alpaca data into Chinese and then generates responses using GPT-4.",
    "The dataset consists of 52K Chinese instructions.",
    "Alpaca GPT4 data zh is the Chinese response version of Alpaca GPT4 data, but it may exhibit semantic shifts during the translation process."
  ]
}